	('a2f3f66c-edac-4821-bc15-dccb215c4de5', 'deac7d01-142f-492e-bf3a-4dfa399bc0e6', 'EVAL', NULL, 'pass', 'LDG GR lever locked in down position, GR Disagree', 'Crosswind, Weather, Injured cabin crew, TURB, COM', 'The EVAL was successful. The MEL Parking Brake Valve was considered in an evacuation without the parking brake. Clear air turbulence required a diversion to MNL, with a continued RNP 06 approach due to cabin crew serious injury conditions, despite considering fuel jettison. A second EVAL involved diverting to CNS due to civil unrest, managing a communication failure, and discontinuing the approach in CNS due to LDG GR Disagree. Good exercise.'),
